	<h1 class="title">他花4000元在西安山里“隐居”，随后出了一本书</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/37534/small/37534.JPG?1421809836" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">石玉 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-16 19:30:22 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/19177/medium/19177.jpg?1450238083" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="19177" data-title="《他花4000元在西安山里“隐居”，随后出了一本书》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/19177/medium/19177.jpg?1450238083" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/19177.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
